name: Kiwee
description:
Kiwee! Fulfill your dreams of finally swinging to the sky as a Kiwi who has mysteriously gained the ability to use a grappling hook! 

Made in 33 hours for WWUJAM XVII

Kiwee sound effects by KaoruHare

CC0 Music from https://opengameart.org/content/up-in-the-sky

Leaderboard from http://dreamlo.com/

Everything else by Ursagames
